This paper deals with a document classification problem using machine learning techniques. The paper proposes a learning framework that can be applied to different models, including linear models and neural networks. The paper also discusses how to optimize evaluation metrics such as accuracy and F1-measure. Based on these characteristics, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
